snippet.title: The Fall Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Enter the world of The Fall! 
Now on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/290770/
Xbox One: https://store.xbox.com/en-CA/Xbox-One/Games/The-Fall/958a7e19-aa24-45b2-a71c-d86298c50454
PS4: https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/the-fall-ps4/
The Humble Store: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/

The Fall is a narrative driven blend of Super Metroid and Monkey Island.

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/OverTheMoonGms
